02:48.795 --> 02:53.402
A tale of two young
outlaws in love.

02:53.688 --> 02:56.443
<i>They were the Bonnie and Clyde
of their day.</i>

02:56.448 --> 02:59.053
<i>Their names were
Bonnie and Clyde.</i>

02:59.116 --> 03:00.253
Miss Bonnie,

03:00.258 --> 03:02.913
might I escort you
to the picture show?

03:02.918 --> 03:04.980
I swear I won't misbehave.

03:04.985 --> 03:06.401
Then no, thank you.

03:06.406 --> 03:07.922
This is Texas,

03:07.925 --> 03:10.343
future home of
Akeem Olajuwon!

03:10.346 --> 03:12.613
And I've got dreams
as big as he will be.

03:12.618 --> 03:14.090
I want action!

03:14.896 --> 03:16.311
Action, eh?

03:18.448 --> 03:19.650
