you want for free!

03:46.585 --> 03:48.433
You're a co-owner!

03:48.516 --> 03:50.772
I'll see you at Thanksgiving!

03:54.916 --> 03:55.690
Oats!

03:55.705 --> 03:58.022
Texas caviar!

04:01.226 --> 04:02.513
Good times.

04:04.685 --> 04:07.193
