Some excitement.

04:07.196 --> 04:10.523
<i>Wow, I guess violence
is her only turn-on.</i>

04:10.527 --> 04:11.503
<i>Well, there might be others,</i>

04:11.508 --> 04:13.233
<i>but I'm too lazy to
figure out what they are.</i>

04:13.237 --> 04:14.611
<i>So violence it is!</i>

04:15.247 --> 04:18.372
Oh, there's somethin'
this kissin' is missin'.

04:23.465 --> 04:26.591
