04:52.486 --> 04:55.981
<i>A nation, crippled by unemployment
and bored by Seabiscuit,</i>

04:55.987 --> 04:58.751
<i>embraces two unlikely folk heroes.</i>

05:00.005 --> 05:03.863
<i>Bonnie and Clyde souvenirs
are flying off the shelves,</i>

05:03.867 --> 05:07.751
<i>and the Dust Bowl duo has
inspired their own radio show.</i>

05:07.755 --> 05:10.302
Uh, Bonnie, where did you
put the money we stole?

05:10.308 --> 05:11.641
I filed it under "G."

05:11.646 --> 05:12.521
Under "G"?

05:12.528 --> 05:14.101
Why would you
file it under "G"?

05:14.106 --> 05:16.510
Because gee, it's swell
to have all that money.

05:16.518 --> 05:17.201
I see.

05:18.256 --> 05:21.842
Their notoriety has reached
the highest levels of government

05:21.847 --> 05:24.693
To deal with the menace
of Bonnie and Clyde,

05:24.698 --> 05:29.460
